[{"id":800,"date":"2012-12-01T22:30:58","date_gmt":"2012-12-01T22:30:58","guid":{"rendered":"http://scott.cloudcontrol.me/?p=800"},"modified":"2017-12-16T20:38:18","modified_gmt":"2017-12-16T20:38:18","slug":"quick-sticky","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://api.scott.ee/journal/quick-sticky/","title":{"rendered":"Quick Sticky"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"intro\">Quick Sticky is a very simple plugin for WordPress that makes it easier to quickly feature or &ldquo;sticky&rdquo; posts from the posts overview screen.</p>\n<p><noscript><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1546\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/scottsweb.mystagingwebsite.com/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?w=900&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"Sticky note posted on a table.\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=250%2C140&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=768%2C429&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=700%2C391&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=120%2C67&amp;ssl=1 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"></noscript><div class=\"lazy\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1546\" src=\"\" alt=\"Sticky note posted on a table.\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" data-src=\"https://i1.wp.com/scottsweb.mystagingwebsite.com/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?w=900&amp;ssl=1\" data-srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=250%2C140&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=768%2C429&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=700%2C391&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i2.wp.com/api.scott.ee/wp-content/uploads/journal-sticky.jpg?resize=120%2C67&amp;ssl=1 120w\"></div></p>\n<p>Working with sticky posts can be a little tricky as the tools are rather hidden within the WordPress interface. Quick Sticky solves this problem.</p>\n<h3>One Sticky Post at a Time</h3>\n<p>On occasions I have also created sites where I have only wanted one sticky post at a time. The plugin contains a filter which allows you to enable this behaviour. Simply add the following snippet of code to your theme functions.php file:</p>\n<pre><code data-language=\"php\">add_filter('qs_one_post_only', '__return_true');</code></pre>\n<p>A demo is available at: <a title=\"WordPress Plugin Demo Site\" href=\"http://wp.scott.ee\">wp.scott.ee</a>. The plugin is open source and released under the <a title=\"WordPress license\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/about/gpl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GNU GPLv2</a>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"abutton btn btn--primary\" title=\"Download Quick Sticky from WordPress.org\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/quick-sticky/\">Download Quick Sticky from WordPress.org</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Quick Sticky is a simple plugin for WordPress that makes it easier to quickly “sticky” posts from the posts overview screen.","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[11],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/800"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=800"}],"version-history":[{"href":"https://api.scott.ee/wp-json/